  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000480/extras/405a9ae1bddf83d0022333b8a633b6b0.poster.avif?t=1742660841\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000480/extras/405a9ae1bddf83d0022333b8a633b6b0.webm?t=1742660841\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2000480/extras/405a9ae1bddf83d0022333b8a633b6b0.mp4?t=1742660841\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Description</h2><strong>\"The Meaning\"</strong> is a first-person psychological horror game focused on tense exploration and immersive storytelling.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Story</h2>In the game, you start with the main protagonist, <strong> Ethen Daniels</strong>, and immediately dive into his story. You'll view his life from his perspective and be submerged in the deep and sad reality of his life. You'll be drawn into Ethen's life and question <strong>the meaning</strong> of yours.<br><br>The game is designed to keep you on your toes and don't let go, so be ready for scary moments and hard to solve mysteries.<br><br>You can expect a thriller story with scary moments, moments full of joy, sadness, uncertainty, and unexpected events.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Game Features</h2><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong> Exploration </strong> - A first-person psychological horror game focused on tense exploration and immersive storytelling.<br></li><li> <strong> Unique storyline </strong> - Enjoy the psychological horror story that has an unexpected twist.<br></li><li> <strong> Hidden Items </strong> - Explore all the different secrets & easter eggs hidden in the game that hint towards a hidden reality that resides within the mundane house. </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong> Immersive Experience </strong> - Realistic 